<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta
      content="minimum-scale=1.0, width=device-width, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no"
      name="viewport"
    />
    <title>이메일 인증번호 발송</title>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@100..900&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <style>
      @charset "UTF-8";
      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: Noto Sans KR, system-ui, Avenir, Helvetica, Arial,
          sans-serif;
        font-weight: 400;
      }
      .container {
        width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .logo {
        width: 120px;
        height: 28px;
        object-fit: contain;
        margin-top: 50px;
      }
      .title {
        color: #161a3f;
        font-size: 26px;
        font-weight: 400;
        letter-spacing: -0.78px;
        margin-top: 16px;
        padding-bottom: 50px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaf4;
      }
      h4 {
        color: #5c5f79;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 400;
        letter-spacing: -0.42px;
        margin-top: 60px;
      }

      h5 {
        color: #161a3f;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: -0.54px;
        margin: 14px 0 40px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .otp {
        width: 400px;
        margin: auto 0;
        padding: 8px;
        background: #eee;
        display: inline-block;
      }

      .otp p {
        text-align: center;
        color: #161a3f;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.84px;
      }

      h6 {
        color: #5c5f79;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        letter-spacing: -0.36px;
        margin: 10px 0 100px;
      }

      .button {
        padding: 14px 48px;
        border: 1px solid #2d40ff;
        background-color: #2d40ff;
        color: #fff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: -0.28px;
      }
      .table-button {
        margin-top: 30px;
        width: 100%;
      }
      .table-button tr td {
        text-align: center;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 50px;
      }
      .footer .phone-icon {
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
        object-fit: contain;
      }
      .footer .phone {
        color: #161a3f;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 500;
        line-height: 22px; /* 91.667% */
        letter-spacing: -0.96px;
        display: inline-block;
      }
      .footer .work-hour {
        color: #161a3f;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 500;
        line-height: 22px;
        vertical-align: top;
        letter-spacing: -0.56px;
      }
      .links span {
        display: inline-block;
        color: #2d40ff;
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 26px;
        letter-spacing: -0.52px;
        margin-top: 30px;
      }
      .info span {
        color: #5b5d75;
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 26px;
        letter-spacing: -0.52px;
        margin-top: 10px;
      }
      .footer-logo {
        margin-top: 11px;
      }
      .footer-logo span {
        color: #5b5d75;
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 26px;
        letter-spacing: -0.52px;
        vertical-align: top;
      }
      .footer-logo img {
        width: 23px;
        height: 23px;
        object-fit: contain;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <img
        class="logo"
        src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/app-snab.appspot.com/o/Frame.jpg?alt=media&token=ed6e3e96-6c5d-4112-b09f-b5ad3fcd470b"
      />
      <h1 class="title">이메일 인증번호 발송</h1>
      <h4>‘(주)시냅틱웨이브’ 에서 본인 확인을 위해 발송되는 메일입니다.</h4>
      <h5>아래 인증번호를 입력하세요</h5>
      <table style="width: 100%">
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td style="text-align: center">
              <div class="otp"><p><%=otp%></p></div>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <h6>이 코드는 15분 동안 유지됩니다</h6>
      <div class="footer">
        <img
          class="phone-icon"
          src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/app-snab.appspot.com/o/phone-solid%201.jpg?alt=media&token=b54df782-3a06-40c5-b630-d58a0e4aeabf"
        />
        <span class="phone">1533-7901</span>
        <span class="work-hour">ㅣ 고객센터 상담시간 (평일) 10:00 ~ 18:00</span>
        <div class="links">
          <span>이용약관 ㅣ개인정보 보호정책 ㅣ위치정보 이용약관</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info">
          <span
            >(주)시냅틱웨이브 ㅣ 대표 : 김세일 ㅣ 사업자등록번호 :
            422-86-01896ㅣ 통신판매신고번호 : 제 2022-안양동안-0425 호ㅣ
            문의메일 : wafl@wafflestay.kr 경기도 안양시 동안구 엘에스로 116번길
            118, 안양2차 SK V1 센터 1030호</span
          >
        </div>
        <div class="footer-logo">
          <img
            src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/app-snab.appspot.com/o/LOGO.jpg?alt=media&token=bd22aa6d-db57-4cea-8bc7-6cdded61602f"
          />
          <span>Copyright ©2024. Wafflestay Inc. All rights reserved.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
